---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | GoZeroShot"
  description="Terms of Service for GoZeroShot engineering services, including permitted use, client responsibilities, and privacy practices."
>
  <main class="main legal-page">
    <section class="legal-shell">
      <a class="back-link" href="/">Back to home</a>
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="effective-date">Effective date: March 23, 2026</p>

      <p>
        GoZeroShot provides software engineering, automation, and applied AI
        services. Some projects may include integrations with third-party
        platforms, including TikTok, when requested by a client or end user.
      </p>

      <h2>Use of the service</h2>
      <p>
        You may use GoZeroShot only in compliance with applicable laws, platform
        policies, and these terms. You are responsible for the materials, content,
        instructions, and credentials you provide for any engagement or connected
        workflow.
      </p>

      <h2>Your account</h2>
      <p>
        You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account and any
        connected third-party accounts. Do not share credentials with unauthorized
        users. You remain responsible for actions taken through your account or
        integrations that you authorize.
      </p>

      <h2>Connected platforms</h2>
      <p>
        GoZeroShot may connect to third-party services such as TikTok to enable
        authentication, profile access, publishing, or other engineering workflows.
        Your use of those services remains subject to their own terms and policies.
      </p>

      <h2>Content and permissions</h2>
      <p>
        You retain ownership of the content, data, and materials you submit. By
        using GoZeroShot, you grant permission to process, store, and transmit
        those materials only as needed to provide the requested engineering or
        automation work.
      </p>

      <h2>Availability</h2>
      <p>
        The service is provided on an &quot;as is&quot; and &quot;as available&quot; basis.
        We may update, suspend, or discontinue features at any time without prior
        notice.
      </p>

      <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, GoZeroShot is not liable for any
        indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or for
        any loss of data, revenue, profits, or business opportunities arising from
        your use of the service.
      </p>

      <h2>Termination</h2>
      <p>
        We may suspend or terminate access to the service if you violate these
        terms, misuse the service, or create risk for us or third-party platforms.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the service
        after updates take effect means you accept the revised terms.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms can be sent to
        <a href="mailto:alynch@gozeroshot.dev">alynch@gozeroshot.dev</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    display: block;
  }

  .legal-shell {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #4a6f98;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }

  .effective-date {
    color: #6b7280;
  }
</style>
